meta.text: Working with children law For the purposes of the definition of working with children law in section 5 of the Children (Education and Care Services) National Law (NSW), the Child Protection (Working with Children) Act 2012 and the regulations made under that Act are declared to be a working with children law for the purposes of the Children (Education and Care Services) National Law (NSW).
